Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up and get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NMy apologies for the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, off we go to celebrate the\Ncompletion of Bojji's training!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us gorge ourselves\Non some fine local fare!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- [BOJJI] Au!\N- [KAGE] Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hold on, Bojji.\NIs that... a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like it's\Npractically the size of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you actually swing\Nsomething that big?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NWhoa-ho-ho! That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NHmm! Hm, hm, hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE grunts] That's not\Na sword, it's a needle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You fraud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You just gave him\Na little rinky-dink sword
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in a giant sheath to make it\Nlook like he'd gotten stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done exactly as\NI said I would do,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've missed the point\Nof the scabbard, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, it creates\Nan impression of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NWhat?! "Missed the point?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that any different\Nfrom what I said, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NBojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There will always be people\Nwho look down upon you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what you\Nmight accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you doubt yourself\Nand look at the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will you meet their gaze?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how to give a nice\Npep talk, but this is reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Hmm. I assure you\Nit's not just talk, Kage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji is far more capable\Nthan you realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NAnd what's more,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,if even you don't believe\Nin him, then who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NUh. You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NBojji...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for doubting\Nyou like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NStill...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] What really\Nhappened in that chamber?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NMm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Much obliged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- [KAGE] Thank you.\N- [BOJJI] Au.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Anyway, is that\Nlittle needle-sword
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,really gonna be\Nany help in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] It will be plenty.\NIf this theory of mine is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji is nigh\Nuntouchable in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Untouchable, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the sound of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then. Let us\Nraise a glass to Bojji
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and his mastery of\Nthe Despa arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Au!\N- [KAGE] Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Despa arts, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMER 10A]\NAh― Ah, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You three again? Do you plan\Nto pick a fight with me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,every time I come to eat here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[ABAN gulping]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Aban, the eldest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the middle one, Layne!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Boan, the youngest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATRONS gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN 05A] The rough\Nand rowdy Aban Brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,just walked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well. Who's\Nyour buddy, there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My apprentice in the art\Nof swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[LAYNE]\N"Swordsmanship"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOAN]\NYour apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean this little\Npipsqueak right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Hey! Who are you guys\Ncallin' a pipsqueak?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[ABAN] What? You have\Na problem with that, friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Do not rise\Nto their bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] That's a shock.\NDespa's playing it cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NAnd Bojji, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that is the mature way\Nto handle these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NYeah. Play it cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think about it,\Nhe's a perfect apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For a camel-faced blowhard\Nlike you, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- [ABAN groans]\N- [CUSTOMER 10B yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] What the heck?!\NHey, Despa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can mock my apprentice\Nall you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but you will not\Ninsult my appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Other way around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMER 10B yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:05:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[ABAN]\NThat was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- [ABAN growls]\N- [DESPA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[LAYNE]\NHeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- [BOAN] Hmph!\N- [DESPA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's weak! Real weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATRONS gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE CUSTOMER 1A0 shrieks]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NWhoa! You're back and... look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there even a bruise on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NHmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[ABAN]\NWhat a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You looking for a fight,\Nlittle boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji! He's too big.\NUse your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] No. There's no need for\Nhim to draw his weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] He will dispatch\Nhis opponent barehanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Despa, how hard did you\Nget hit with that tray?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Have faith and observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can\Nmess with me, runt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[ABAN]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,His punch didn't do\Nanything to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NWait. He's laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji landed a punch\Nand he's laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[ABAN groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- [PATRONS gasping]\N- [DESPA] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[CUSTOMER]\NDid you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- [LAYNE, BOAN] Aban!\N- [BOJJI sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ABAN]\NStay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell\Ndid you do to me, kid...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.59,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As living creatures,\Nwe have weak points
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll pound you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Little runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NTake the jaw, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a relatively light blow\Ncan jolt the brain hard enough
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to induce a concussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:07:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] To make up for\Nhis own lack of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,he utilizes his foe's momentum―\Nand lands a precise hit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to their weak spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the\Nmagnificence of Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NDespa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[sniffles]\NI'll never doubt you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You little creep...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What kinda trick did you pull?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- [KAGE gasps]\N- Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you've taken\Nyour weapon in hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,are you ready and willing\Nto escalate this petty squabble
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,into a fight to the death?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NBojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Draw your blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[ABAN snarls]\NLittle bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NGet up, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE whimpers]\NBojji just killed that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Expertly done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's out cold,\Nbut very much alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji knocked him out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Now get him\Nout of here, you louts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NI still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How did Bojji take him down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NMm. Allow me to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Owie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NEh? Did that even hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Though the needle may not\Nhave pierced my skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it did prick a pain receptor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Receptor"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. And conversely...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NWaugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?! Why?!\N- [wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- What did you do?!\N- [wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- [whimpering]\N- [wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you avoid the pain receptors,\Nit doesn't hurt in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't break any\Nblood vessels, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stop?\NThat's really gross-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Living creatures are marvels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We are complex, and complex\Nthings have many points
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of failure, which Bojji\Nhas learned quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To knock an opponent\Nunconscious, one must cause
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the brain to fail momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] One can bring\Nthe brain to a gentle halt
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,by briefly cutting off\Nthe flow of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,With his needle-sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji can stimulate his foe's\Nnerve endings directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,while avoiding\Ntheir vital organs,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,causing their blood\Nvessels to dilate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The resulting drop in blood\Npressure starves the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of oxygen, leading to\Nloss of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NUh... Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Put simply, Bojji has the\Nability to incapacitate
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,an opponent without\Ncausing lasting damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE gasps]\NThat's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome, Bojji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This sword style\Nis perfect for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Furthermore...\NUsing that same skill,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,he can bring the machinery of\Nan opponent's body
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to a permanent halt\Nwith minimal exertion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NWhoa... Bojji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have gotten stronger.\NI should be happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA chuckles]\NA-Are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kage, what kind of strength\Nhave you been searching for
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- all this time?\N- [KAGE] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the pursuit of\Nthis great strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is your intention not\Nto protect others?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The sword of a king,\Nable to save the meek
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and shame the mighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this not exactly the power\Nyou've been seeking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're right. I did want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, powerful people\Ncan have weak hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji will not be\Ncorrupted by his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mental fortitude was the\Nfoundation of his training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji. One who bears a sword\Nmust obey three rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rule one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Au, au!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rule two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAwau, au!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:11:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NRule three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAu, awah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Hmm! You must etch\Nthose words into your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE sobs] Bojji...\NI'm so proud right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Despa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch those?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultimately, Bojji's strength\Ncomes from the righteousness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,already in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bojji, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Au-ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] So long as you always\Nbear those rules firmly in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,your abilities will only grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As will your strength\Nin body and mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] You will lead\Na joyous existence that shines
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,like a beacon to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah!\N- [DESPA] Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever onward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Au, au, au.\N- Thank you for everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Despa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then...\NShall we feast, gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE sighs]\NI'm totally stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Hmm. Uh, why don't the\Ntwo of you go ahead without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one small matter\NI need to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE]\NHuh? See ya, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN 05A]\NAttention!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Oh. Please,\Nthat's entirely unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN 05A]\NAt ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't need to go for\Nthe face a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you did, which is exactly\Nwhat I asked you to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and I got to see how Bojji\Nperforms in real combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NFor your trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...\N[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to confess,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expected to be\Nso completely outmatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA]\NHmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment he grabbed his sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized right away\NI couldn't beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN 05A] Then you've got\Nwork to do when we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break\Njust this once, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN 05A laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA chuckles]\NThough, in truth, today offered
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,barely a glimpse\Nof Bojji's true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[CAPTAIN 05A]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, he's acquired\Nanother skill
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that's even more impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[DESPA] Though I don't expect\Nhe's going to be putting it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,on display terribly often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAGE] Hey Bojji.\NWhen I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you learned how to strike\Nyour opponents' weak spots
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,thanks to Despa's training,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but you've always been quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How in the world\Ndid you get so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Au, au.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Mitsumata taught you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, the big snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, Prince. Nicely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, you've much to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NAh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You are still relying\Non your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You must sharpen\Nyour other senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[MITSUMATA]\NUntil your sense of touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...can detect\Neven unseen hazards...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...through the movement of\Nthe air against your skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Au!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN]\NNews from the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A pack of underworld\Nmonsters attacked
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Hiling's chambers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorshe put his life at\Nhazard to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, it appears the\NMirror left for the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,King Bosse has taken no action.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, Master Apeas\Nis standing guard
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,over the Underworld portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN sighs] There's no way\NI can do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you speak\Nas if we weren't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] I am the Snake Handler,\Nand you're all more precious
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to me than words can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you in harm's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[MITSUMATA]\NFor you, Master Bebin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...we would do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN]\NAnd Prince Bojji?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm told that\Nhis training is now complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and that he's grown a great deal\Nstronger in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Despa is a master of his craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[MITSUMATA]\NIndeed. He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN]\NHmm. So, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Bojji...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN] I understand that\Nyou owe quite a heavy debt
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to Prince Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I believe\NPrince Daida is more fit
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for the throne by far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems I'm not\Nalone in that belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your decision to train Bojji\Nand teach him to read lips
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,has been met with skepticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. Prince Bojji's\Nstrength may never rise
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to the caliber of a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As the boy grows,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I know with certainty that\Nhe will save many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact... Prince Daida himself\Nwill be counted among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Bojji will save\NPrince Daida?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] Is that a prophecy\Nor wild intuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a feeling,\Nbut one I do not doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEBIN]\NHmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The king's return...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That may well be where\Nthis all ends up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if Mitsumata is the one\Nwho trained you, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...that means Bebin probably\Nknows what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOJJI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like this. Bebin told me\Nthis before we left the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, your kingdom\Nhas gotten wrapped up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in some huge conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]\NAu, ah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, and I have no idea\Nhow it's gonna play out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But... he told me\NI needed to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Know this. I serve King Daida.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My loyalty is to him above all\Nothers and I have no intention
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of handing his crown\Nover to Prince Bojji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In time, you'll come to\Nunderstand why I would do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Bojji... Where\Ndo we go from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you return to your kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:18:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
